OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FVarying, often large amounts,
OL,6,Fof thin cloud but still bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells will occur. Slightly
OL,8,Fcooler along the coast with onshore
OL,9,Fwinds, becoming very warm or locally
OL,10,Fhot inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,13,Fand bright Saturday, very warm or
OL,14,Flocally hot. Sunday outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fclearing then scattered possibly heavy
OL,16,Fshowers, feeling noticeably cooler.
OL,17,FMonday generally dry, sunny spells
OL,18,Fwith average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
